Package nom.tam.fits.compression.algorithm.uncompressed

package nom.tam.fits.compression.algorithm.uncompressed
( for internal use) Compression algorithm, for non compressing at all. It's weird, I know, and it's weirder that it's a package by itself, but that's life.
